  switzerland: `M 460.906 357.427 L 463.097 345.01 C 463.097 345.01 470.401 337.949 472.593 336.975 C 474.784 336.001 482.575 332.836 487.445 332.105 C 492.314 331.375 503.271 328.836 506.436 328.836 C 509.601 328.836 517.251 326.505 518.854 326.262 C 520.457 326.018 536.628 330.644 538.332 331.131 C 540.036 331.618 560.916 337.445 560.916 337.445 L 557.472 344.331 L 557.472 351.562 L 561.949 356.687 L 561.949 356.687 L 561.949 356.687 L 564.216 355.814 L 566.08 356.687 C 566.08 356.687 568.022 358.931 568.271 359.51 C 568.52 360.09 569.619 364.777 569.619 364.777 L 585.049 356.687 L 585.049 368.434 L 590.528 376.698 L 588.634 384.101 L 581.231 383.757 L 573.311 379.827 L 570.212 382.38 L 569.921 390.715 L 569.524 392.71 L 566.597 392.021 L 564.163 391.755 L 559.646 392.073 L 555.067 392.624 L 552.318 392.71 L 552.318 389.783 L 545.421 385.823 L 544.215 390.816 L 535.951 392.71 L 524.589 381.002 L 520.457 379.827 L 516.841 379.827 L 513.053 381.534 L 509.266 383.241 L 504.271 390.376 L 497.559 399.08 L 494.675 398.383 L 488.419 396.871 L 481.947 387.987 L 480.402 384.639 L 480.627 379.827 L 481.151 378.101 L 480.871 376.175 L 480.871 376.175 L 480.091 374.217 L 481.107 370.132 L 482.118 367.349 L 482.575 365.218 L 478.923 361.566 L 473.229 359.907 L 465.501 358.405 Z`
